    CaDSBase
    Basis class of the gripper development enviorment Root of the gripper initalization for: - CaDSBase.SIMULATION: Simulation environment - CaDSBase.REAL: Lego Gripper

    Implements functionality for the Button provided by the lego brick
    CaDSEV3Motors

    Implements the grapper grap and release functionality
    CaDSEVGripper
